 results imply new lower and\nupper bounds for the Dirichlet energy (one-constant Oseen-Frank energy) of\nreflection-symmetric tangent unit-vector fields in a rectangular prism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jul 2009 20:09:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-07-06"}
