ast is overestimated in the models and that its\natmosphere responds to the seasonal forcing with a greater inertia than\nexpected.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Jul 2009 12:01:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-07-17"}
