etween radio luminosity Lr, Lx, and M. The unified model for\nSeyfert galaxies seems to hold, showing in hard X-rays that the central engine\nis the same in Seyfert 1 and 2, but seen under different inclination angles and\nabsorption. (Abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Jul 2009 15:34:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Aug 2009 10:10:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
